    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-black mb-1">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-ink/50 text-sm">Effective date: 21 June 2026 · Applies to thaiholidaybudget.com</p>

    <p>This Cookie Policy explains how thaiholidaybudget.com uses cookies and similar technologies. We keep this to the bare minimum needed to make the estimator work. We do not use tracking cookies, advertising cookies, or third-party analytics.</p>

    <h2>1. What are cookies and local storage?</h2>
    <p>Cookies are small text files a website can store in your browser. "Local storage" is a related browser technology that stores small amounts of data on your device. Both can be used to remember information between page loads. <strong>Our own</strong> features rely on local storage for strictly functional purposes; in addition, our advertising partner Adsterra may set third-party cookies, as described in Section 3.</p>

    <h2>2. What we use, and why</h2>
    <p>The items below are essential to the Service and are stored on your device only — they are never transmitted to a server we control.</p>
    <table>
      <tr><th>Name</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Type</th><th>Duration</th></tr>
      <tr><td>somchai_pattaya_v1</td><td>Saves your in-progress estimate so it is available when you return</td><td>Strictly necessary · local storage</td><td>Until you reset or clear site data</td></tr>
      <tr><td>somchai_cookie_ok</td><td>Remembers that you dismissed the cookie notice</td><td>Strictly necessary · local storage</td><td>Until you clear site data</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p>These are classified as strictly necessary because, without them, the estimator could not save your progress or respect your notice preference.</p>

    <h2>3. Advertising cookies (Adsterra)</h2>
    <p>The Service is free and supported by advertising served through <strong>Adsterra</strong>. To serve, cap, and measure ads — and, where you allow it, to personalise them — Adsterra and its partners may set and read cookies and similar identifiers in your browser. These are set by Adsterra, not by us, and we do not have access to the information they collect.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Common examples include Adsterra's advertising and frequency-capping cookies set by its ad-serving partners.</li>
      <li>If you do not consent to personalised advertising, Adsterra may still serve non-personalised ads, which use cookies for frequency capping, aggregated reporting, and fraud/abuse prevention.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can review how Adsterra uses data in advertising in the <a href="https://adsterra.com/privacy-policy/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">Adsterra Privacy Policy</a>, and manage vendor choices at <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">aboutads.info/choices</a> or, in the EU, <a href="https://www.youronlinechoices.eu/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">youronlinechoices.eu</a>.</p>

    <h2>4. What we do not use</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>No first-party analytics or behavioural profiling run by us.</li>
      <li>No social-media tracking pixels.</li>
      <li>We do not combine ad data with the budget figures you enter — those never leave your device.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Third-party content delivery</h2>
    <p>The Service loads open-source libraries and fonts from public content-delivery networks (Tailwind CSS and Chart.js via jsDelivr/Cloudflare, and Google Fonts). Those providers may set their own cookies or process your IP address as part of delivering those files, under their own policies, which we do not control. See our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> for more on third parties.</p>

    <h2>5. Managing your preferences</h2>
    <p>You are in control of both the functional storage and the advertising cookies:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Use the in-page cookie banner or the <a href="/cookie-settings">Cookie Settings</a> page to set your advertising preference and review what is stored.</li>
      <li>Review Adsterra&rsquo;s advertising privacy practices in the <a href="https://adsterra.com/privacy-policy/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">Adsterra Privacy Policy</a>.</li>
      <li>Use the <strong>Reset</strong> button inside the estimator to wipe your saved estimate instantly.</li>
      <li>Clear your browser's site data for this domain, or use a private/incognito window, to remove or avoid stored data.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>If we change how local storage or cookies are used, we will update this page and the effective date above.</p>

    <h2>7. Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions can be sent to <a href="mailto:support@thaiholidaybudget.com">support@thaiholidaybudget.com</a>.</p>
